      <title>俄罗斯能源精英和印度官员试图保持石油供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/india-energy-week-gathering-will-seek-to-keep-cheap-russian-oil-flowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，全球第三大石油进口国印度将在国际高管和政府官员的聚会上讨论能源安全问题，因为这个世界第三大石油进口国要应对红海紧张局势、对俄罗斯更严厉的制裁以及即将到来的大选的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/india-energy-week-gathering-will-seek-to-keep-cheap-russian-oil-flowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:30:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
